title: Pampers Aqua Pure Sensitive Baby Wipes 6X Pop-Top 336 Count
description: Our simplest formula, Pampers Aqua Pure baby wipes are made with 99% purified water. Perfect for sensitive skin, Aqua Pure water wipes are hypoallergenic and free of alcohol, fragrance, parabens and latex for a soft and gentle clean. Aqua Pure wipes help restore skin’s pH better than the leading super-premium baby wipe. Plus, each pack includes our handy 1-Wipe POP TOPTM, which keeps wipes from drying out. From Pampers, the #1 pediatrician recommended brand. For purely healthy skin, use Pampers Aqua Pure wipes together with Pampers Pure Protection diapers. (No rubbing alcohol and no natural rubber latex)
